# Liabilities Insurance Reinsurance Deposit Component Fair Value Amount

## identifier
de4795

## type
float

## definition
Report the fair value of the contractual obligation in relation to the deposit (investment) component of insurance policies that have been ceded under reinsurance as at the relevant date.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.ReinsuranceDepositComponentFairValue.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
